A text editor is a software application or program that is used for creating, editing, and manipulating plain text files. Text editors are essential tools for anyone working with text-based documents, programming code, or markup languages like HTML, XML, or Markdown. They are commonly used by programmers, web developers, writers, and anyone who needs to work with text-based content.

